{"tid":2325427,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【新聞智庫】鬼滅經濟學","createTime":"2020-12-14T14:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T09:59:28.000Z","uid":248417,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"026bdc5b5fa6a679bac99ea20a31f312fd926a51","tid":2325427,"uid":248417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXtKTEUJ.jpg&amp;h=4a3cdcc1&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】日本超人氣動漫《鬼滅之刃》熱潮持續燃燒，不僅電影和漫畫爆紅，周邊商品大賣，更被視為當前日本經濟的救星。<br />\n<br />\n話題之作《鬼滅之刃》自去年播出動畫版後，人氣不斷飆升，劇場版電影十月在日本上映後，更將熱潮推至高峰。全套漫畫長期佔據銷量榜首的位置，累積銷量達到1.2億本，結局單行本發售更掀起搶購潮，日本全國書店大排長龍。<br />\n<br />\n引人入勝的情節，吸引了大量日本人進戲院捧場，破盡票房紀錄，包括<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">打破動畫大師宮崎駿作品《千與千尋》最快突破三百億日圓的紀錄</span></span>，成為新票房神話。<br />\n<br />\n漫畫衍生出無限商機，與不同品牌合作，推出的周邊商品林林總總，無論是零食抑或是服飾，只要是跟《鬼滅》聯乘，都會大受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n《鬼滅》帶動的觀光熱潮亦不容忽視，許多粉絲專程到類似故事場景的景點朝聖「打卡」，帶旺人流。以別府市與主角同姓的神社為例，十月底的到訪人數比去年同期激增一百倍。<br />\n<br />\n日本在過去一年飽受新冠疫情困擾，加上東京奧運未能如期舉行，內需疲弱，旅遊業受重創。在前景黯淡之際，《鬼滅》電影正好帶來曙光，成為疫市下日本經濟的靈丹。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，《鬼滅之刃》之所以會大熱，同疫情下「宅經濟」不無關係。《鬼滅》系列動畫相繼在電視和網上串流平台播放，民眾足不出戶就可以接觸到，加上荷李活大製作押後上映，缺少競爭對手的《鬼滅之刃》自然脫穎而出。有專家估計，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>經濟效益至少達到二千億日圓</strong></span></span>，即相當於大約149億港元。<br />\n<br />\n《鬼滅》來勢洶洶，引發的熱潮亦吹到政圈，就連首相菅義偉都要緊貼潮流，引用漫畫台詞回應議員質詢。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉：「請容許我用「全集中呼吸」回答質詢。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416569&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n1DApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=912ebbfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416569&h=9af9ee71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416569</a><br />\n<br />\n日本政府不如唔好搞奧運，直接改做鬼滅專題活動，可能仲賺過垃圾奧運呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d778551f14ee2b14d50e2111d1b001c56280586a","tid":2325427,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"加上荷李活大製作押後上映，缺少競爭對手<br />\n<br />\n重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8683134a07506cbfe4f5f61aeb6e4fadcf1a12cc","tid":2325427,"uid":200529,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:27:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾經濟學"},{"pid":"0b616528e64709936bf89b21b916442dc5090e23","tid":2325427,"uid":292497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"Nezuko<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ce2bc9699e4c120da104cf38e25d9a5f3a1ef6","tid":2325427,"uid":200529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"見到成班冇睇開動漫嘅海鮮又係cos鬼滅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2553e1e3a45bbe46623bef71c435efb9d3251a4","tid":2325427,"uid":140263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"改奧運吉祥物做炭治郎算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a417097a788ab4fdca8f8d6c3ab6d6e72bc0e90","tid":2325427,"uid":248417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d778551f14ee2b14d50e2111d1b001c56280586a","tid":2325427,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"加上荷李活大製作押後上映，缺少競爭對手<br />\n<br />\n重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"同期對手好似得Fate HF同京紫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0762a789ceaf58e630007b831098916f562